    "Zelfs met maximale wekelijkse groei is de piekbelasting niet haalbaar vóór de racedag. Bespreek dit met je coach." : {
      "extractionState" : "stale",
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Selbst mit maximalem wöchentlichem Zuwachs ist die Spitzenbelastung vor dem Renntag nicht erreichbar. Besprich das mit deinem Coach."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Even with maximum weekly growth, the peak load isn't achievable before race day. Discuss this with your coach."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Incluso con el máximo crecimiento semanal, la carga máxima no es alcanzable antes del día de carrera. Coméntalo con tu entrenador."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Zonder Apple Health kan VibeCoach je Vibe Score en herstel niet berekenen. Je kunt het later koppelen via Instellingen." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Ohne Apple Health kann VibeCoach deinen Vibe Score und deine Erholung nicht berechnen. Du kannst es später in den Einstellungen verbinden."
          }
        },
        "en" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Without Apple Health, VibeCoach can't compute your Vibe Score and recovery. You can connect it later in Settings."
          }
        },
        "es" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Sin Apple Health, VibeCoach no puede calcular tu Vibe Score ni tu recuperación. Puedes conectarlo más tarde en Ajustes."
          }
        }
      }
    },
